          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "請輸入自訂文字圖示的字級（磅值），例如 13。留空則使用預設字級。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Please enter standard [date format patterns](https://unicode.org/reports/tr35/tr35-dates.html#Date_Format_Patterns) here. Refer to the [wiki](https://github.com/LunarBar-app/LunarBar/wiki) for more instructions and examples.": {
